clause_text: (2) 4) Provided further that, for the purpose of Regulation 7.6.1 and 7.6.2, incentive FSI shall be allowed for redevelopment of building which were existing in Gram Panchyat areas before their enclusion in ULB for any Regional Development Authority subject to following conditions :-
